SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260304T063600
DTEND:20260304T074800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.796ft at 06:36\n-2.948ft at 07:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Meager pulse of fresh WNW swell to lap in with knee-thigh high waves on th
 e lower tides. \n\nWinds are offshore NW through the day\, light in the mo
 rning then picking up to moderate over the afternoon\, keeping town spots 
 offshore.
END:VEVENT
