BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260305T063600
DTEND:20260305T085400
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.078ft at 06:36\n-2.957ft at 08:54\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Shorter to mid period NW swell mix picks up. The shorter period will limit
  size a bit for Santa Cruz\, but it still looks good for fun waist to shou
 lder high range waves\, showing most size in the afternoon on the ebbing t
 ide. There will also be a little underlying S Southern Hemi pulse helping 
 then.\n\nLight northerly wind is currently expected in the morning\, becom
 ing moderate NW for the afternoon. Conditions in town should stay clean or
  at least semi clean all day. 
END:VEVENT
